    "All these parameters represent values sequentially sensed and calculated for each column.",
    "The detail of VMM operation using CA is demonstrated in the 'Method' section.",
    "The experimental and calculated VMM results matched well regardless of the defective cell portion, demonstrating that each CA case (D0, D30, and D50) is suitable for the VMM operation without any interference between cells owing to the characteristics of the SRM.",
